eu.amidst.dynamic.learning.parametric

Interface ParameterLearningAlgorithm

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BayesianLearningAlgorithm
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ParallelMaximumLikelihood, ParallelMLMissingData, SVB

    public interface ParameterLearningAlgorithm
    This interface defines the Dynamic Bayesian learning algorithm for DynamicBayesianNetwork models.
